CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 17, 1965, pg. 24 reads: "Gabfest - Diamond talk was the order of the day at Forbes Field, on Monday, prior to the beginning of the opening day game between the Pirates and the Giants... In the right photo, Al McBean (left) and Andre Rodgers (right) quiz Orlando Cepeda of the Giants about the condition of his knee. Capeda, who wasn't in the Giants' opening-day lineup, is still recuperating from an operation on his knee, this past winter. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Pirates baseball player Al McBean, San Francisco Giants Orlando Cepeda, and Pirates Andre Rodgers, posed on Forbes Field for 1965 season opener
